Date time module can be used for the following when programming;
     1. Sheduling tasks, 
     2. Calculating time difference,	
     3. Converting between time zones,
     4. Formatting dates and times,
     5. Creating calenders,
     6. Calculating holidays,
     7. Time series analysis,
     8. Getting timestamps of activities in an application,
     9. Adding posts on a blog, among others. 
